Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.58,0:16:21.25,TEXT CN,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.54,0:16:24.37,TEXT CN,,0,0,0,,斯圖亞特·阿蓋爾少尉
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.69,0:16:25.33,TEXT CN,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 1,0:16:28.89,0:16:30.59,TEXT CN,,0,0,0,,蓋爾·馬卡蘭上尉
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.09,0:16:34.30,TEXT CN,,0,0,0,,當然了 長官
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.30,0:16:35.63,TEXT CN,,0,0,0,,這是我的榮幸
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.49,0:16:42.36,TEXT CN,,0,0,0,,上尉…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.87,0:16:45.36,TEXT CN,,0,0,0,,馬卡蘭上尉正在巡邏
